@lukecwik See the stack trace in BEAM-2223.

It is plausible that we could wrap the [ClassLoader](https://github.com/apache/beam/blob/master/sdks/java/core/src/main/java/org/apache/beam/sdk/options/PipelineOptionsFactory.java#L606) invocations directly, but given that we get `Error` thrown in various places it seemed safer to have a catch-all at the front door.

Thoughts?
